text: "Whatzupwitu" is a song by American singer and musician Eddie Murphy, released in 1993. The track is notable for its upbeat vibe and features a collaboration with the legendary musician Michael Jackson. The song combines elements of R&B; and pop, and its lyrics express themes of love and togetherness.
